title: #92Noon! Talkers/Bercich/Siny/Dilfer/Fleck
description: Riding emotions of a couple undefeated teams to start the show with Gopher football and the Wolves. Pete Bercich in studio, followed by Dave Sinykin and the border battle update. Former QB/Super Bowl winner Trent Dilfer is on the hotline, and Gophers HC PJ Fleck makes his weekly pit-stop #92Noon!
